{
  "name": "Fighting Spirit",
  "type": "feature",
  "img": "icons/skills/social/intimidation-impressing.webp",
  "system": {
    "description": "<p>You stand ready for Combat at any moment, granting you the following benefits:</p><ul><li><p><strong>Combat Readiness:</strong> At the start of your first turn in Combat, you gain one of the following benefits:</p><ul><li><p><strong>Fortify:</strong> You gain the benefits of the Dodge Action and ADV on the next Save you make.</p></li><li><p><strong>Advance:</strong> You gain the benefits of the Move Action and ADV on the next Martial Attack or Physical Check you make.</p></li></ul></li><li><p><strong>Second Wind:</strong> Once per Combat when you start your turn <strong>Bloodied</strong>, you can regain 2 HP and 2 SP.</p></li></ul><p></p><p><em><strong>System Tip:</strong> Roll this item to trigger <strong>Combat Readiness.</strong></em></p>",
